Title: The Mistake
Plot: House and Chase find themselves in a serious situation after a young mother with stomach pains dies. Months later, Stacy counsels Chase prior to his disciplinary hearing, and must determine whether Chase made a mistake that ultimately led to the patient's death. She soon realizes he is holding something back.
ParentalRatingReason: R13 Violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Greg Winter, Sammi Hanratty, Kate Enggren, Adair Tishler, Licia Shearer, Ryan Hurst, Kevin Moon, Sterling Beaumon, John Lafayette, Allison Smith, John Rubenstein
